Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: A Wonderful Work or a Rat Trap?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00szs7j
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 16 Jun 2000
In light of a new vedict surrounding the visiting rights of grandparents, Alistair Cooke reflects on the pace at which the Supreme Court makes its decisions.